The paper discusses privacy in cryptocurrencies, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses incentives and how they could be used to encourage users to adopt privacy-preserving implementations, which could fall under the categories of cybernetics (cs.CY), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), game theory (cs.GT), and machine learning (cs.LG).
